// A 4/4 with both trample and deathtouch — exercises [CR#702.19b] with the
// [CR#702.2] lethal-damage shortcut: deathtouch makes lethal = 1 per blocker,
// so the trampler can assign 1 to each blocker and spill the rest to the
// defending player. Two keywords in one `abilities` list (confirms multi-keyword
// loading).
Normal(
    name: "Trample Deathtouch Creature",
    mana_cost: [Generic(2), Black, Green],
    types: [Creature],
    power: 4,
    toughness: 4,
    abilities: [Keyword(Trample), Keyword(Deathtouch)],
)
